+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01359ZbggnkFTSUhxXTshfjR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No existing checkpoints and the src directory is empty. Since this is a non-interactive benchmark environment, I'll proceed directly with autopilot mode.\n\n**Non-interactive mode: using Autopilot.**\n\nLet me make key design decisions and then proceed to implementation.\n\n**Design Decisions:**\n\nQ: Route structure?\n→ RESTful with `/auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/folders`, `/documents`, `/share`, `/activity`\n  Reasoning: Clear, intuitive, matches the spec suggestions.\n\nQ: Permission resolution algorithm?\n→ Max-permission wins across all paths (direct + folder inheritance)\n  Reasoning: Spec says \"most permissive role granted.\"\n\nQ: Data structures?\n→ Maps with string UUIDs as keys for all entities\n  Reasoning: O(1) lookup, TypeScript-friendly.\n\nQ: Token format?\n→ Simple UUID-based tokens stored in a Map<token, userId>\n  Reasoning: No JWT needed, in-memory is fine for this scope.\n\nNow let me invoke the TDD skill to implement this properly."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":320,"cache_read_input_tokens":22315,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":320},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"92580e83-ab2c-4ee7-b38c-9a68f0de93e9","uuid":"3bfd6d4b-a249-496d-90ff-aa1581f255e1"}
